data: ヽ༼ຈل͜ຈ༽ﾉ гคเรє ๏г ๔เє ヽ༼ຈل͜ຈ༽ﾉ
description: “Raise your dongers” was originally a catch phrase by League of Legends player Michael Santana. He likes to play as the LoL champion Heimerdinger who he has nicknamed “donger”. The actual phrase “raise your dongers” along with the original donger emoticon ヽ༼ຈل͜ຈ༽ﾉ came from a tweet by Michael Santana in June of 2013. Since then there have been many other emoticons made in this style with ༼ and ༽ for the sides of the face.
